               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-1493" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1493" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1493" type="surname" value="ANDERSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1493" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ANDERSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a surgeon. I attended Mr. Ilderton—he had a wound on the right temple, rather more than an inch long, and completely dividing the scalp down to the bone—it bled largely—it was of a dangerous character, but is now healing.</p>
